Package com.redhat.victims

Class Summary
ArtifactLocator Helper methods to locate local and remote JAR files.
Checksum Mechanism for creating fingerprints compatible with those in the victims database.
IOUtils A collection of miscellaneous utilities used throughout the plug-in to format output.
Resources Basic resource bundle for messages and formating.
Settings Configuration settings are defined and stored by this class.
Synchronizer The VictimClient class provides the mechanism for synchronizing data within a local Victims database with the remote canonical server.
VictimsRule This class is the main entry point for working with the Maven Enforcer plug-in.
 

Exception Summary
VictimsException Generic wrapper for all exceptions that are thrown within this plug-in.
